a card "is face up" if its direction is up
a card "is face down" if its direction is down

to turn a card face up: set the direction of the card to up
to turn a card face down: set the direction of the card to down

to flip a card over:
	if its direction is up then turn it face down
	otherwise turn it face up

to move a card to a pile
	remove the card from its pile
	add the card to the pile
	set the pile of the card to the pile